('dornier228','Flightcrew of two. 100 - Typical passenger seating for 15. 212 - Typical passenger seating for 19 at two abreast and 76cm (30in) pitch. 228212 based 228 Cargo has a max payload of 2340kg (5159lb). 212 based ambulance accommodates six stretchers and up to nine attendants or passengers.',NULL,NULL),
('dornier328','Flightcrew of two. Typical passenger seating for 30 to 33 at three abreast, max seating for 39 at four abreast.',NULL,NULL),
