('embraeremb120brasilia','Flightcrew of two. Standard main cabin seating for 30 at three abreast and 79cm (31in) pitch. Optional passenger seating for 24 or 26 with greater baggage/cargo space. Alternative interior arrangements for executive and cargo roles.',NULL,NULL),
('embraeremb121xingu','Xingu I - Flightcrew of one or two, plus typical main cabin seating for five or six passengers. Xingu II - Flightcrew of two. Main cabin seating for seven, eight or nine passengers, depending on customer preference.',NULL,NULL),
